求你了, 不要让我回到那去
Just, please, don't make me go back there.

326
00:21:07,851 --> 00:21:11,354
事实上, 我很好. 我感觉非常好.
Really, I'm fine. I feel perfectly fine.

327
00:21:12,772 --> 00:21:14,315
Weir博士, 我是Sheppard.
Dr. Weir, this is Sheppard.

328
00:21:14,983 --> 00:21:19,279
Peterson已经同意回到医学实验室
