Peterson has agreed to go back to the med lab
until we can get the situation resolved.

329
00:21:19,863 --> 00:21:20,739
站住!
Stop!

330
00:21:34,794 --> 00:21:35,754
噢, 天哪!
Oh, my god!

331
00:21:35,879 --> 00:21:36,921
他中枪了
He's been shot.

332
00:21:36,963 --> 00:21:38,214
发生什么了?
What's going on?

333
00:22:01,404 --> 00:22:02,614
发生什么了?
What's going on?

334
00:22:02,655 --> 00:22:04,366
古人的控制器没有反映了
Ancient controls are unresponsive.

335
00:22:04,824 --> 00:22:07,535
我接到报告Peterson已经被传送到了餐厅了
I'm getting reports that Peterson
transported into the mess hall.

336
00:22:07,744 --> 00:22:09,746
处于某种原因, 我们无法跟着他
For some reason, we can't follow him.

337
00:22:09,788 --> 00:22:11,081
这个城市被接管了...
The city has taken over...

338
